0w Lamp</h1><img src="images/content/powerplantMH.jpg" alt=""><dl><dt>Maker</dt><dd>Powerplant</dd></dl><p>PowerPlant lamps are tailored to promote optimum development at each plant growth stage. Use in vegative cycle.</p></article><article class="module column product"><h1>Powerplant Super HPS 600w Lamp</h1><img src="images/content/powerplantHPS.jpg" alt=""><dl><dt>Maker</dt><dd>Powerplant</dd></dl><p>PowerPlant lamps are tailored to promote optimum development at each plant growth stage. Use in flowering cycle.</p></article><article class="module column product"><h1>Lucagrow HPS 600w Lamp</h1><img src="images/content/lucagrow.jpg" alt=""><dl><dt>Maker</dt><dd>GE Lighting</dd></dl><p>The G.E Lucagrow HPS 600W lamp offers a complete natural light substitute. With a long life of up to 28,500 hours, the lucagrow high output lamps give up to 20% more light than standard high pressure sodium lamps. The Lucagrow lamp maintains 90% light output over the life of the lamp and is fully interchangeable with other HPS lamps. The 600W Lucagrow lamp will put out 90,000 lumens with a colour temperature of 2,000K.</p></article><article class="module column product"><h1>Son T HPS 600w Lamp</h1><img src="images/content/sont600.jpg" alt=""><dl><dt>Maker</dt><dd>Phillips</dd></dl><p>The Philips Son-T Plus 600W Lamp is a high quality high-pressure sodium lamp with PIA (Philips Intergrated Antenna) technology for increased reliability and lower early failure rates, with reliable ignition throughout its lifetime. It improves output and profitability in all sectors of crop production by generating a spectrum with enhanced blue output, optimising plant development and quality with good leaf and bloom colour with extra branching. Its high luminous efficiency of up to 150 lm/W makes this the most efficient Son-T Lamp.</p></article><article class="module column product"><h1>Son T Agro HPS 400w Lamp</h1><img src="images/content/sontagro.jpg" alt=""><dl><dt>Maker</dt><dd>Phillips</dd></dl><p>Th